Application Components
    ├── Web Frontend
    │    ├── HTML, CSS, JavaScript
    │    ├── Django Templates (for rendering dynamic content)
    │    └── User Interaction: Form Submissions, Viewing Data, Editing Data
    │
    └── Server (Backend)
         ├── Django Framework (Python)
         │    ├── URL Routing (urls.py)
         │    ├── Views (views.py)
         │    │    ├── Handle user requests (CRUD operations)
         │    │    └── Authentication, Role-Based Access
         │    ├── Models (models.py)
         │    │    └── Interact with the Database (WorkRecords, Clients, Users)
         │    └── Admin Interface
         │         ├── Full control over the system (via `/admin`)
         │         └── Managed by Administrators and Directors
         │
         └── Database
              ├── PostgreSQL (or SQLite for development)
              ├── Tables: Users, WorkRecords, Clients, WorkTypes
              └── Handles Data Storage, Retrieval, and Updates
